From cou.: 7 As a first step, to shed some light on the conformations sampled by the reduced form of the rotaxane shown in Fig. 1b, we performed a MD simulation of 100 ns at 298 K in an NVT ensemble and in acetonitrile (i.e.CH3CN) dilute solution.21 Such a simulation was started considering the molecular shuttle at the centre of a rectangular box of 21 nm3 filled with solvent molecules at the typical liquid density of 782.2 kg m−3 (see Fig. 1 reported in ESI†).21 In this respect, in line with experimental findings,13 we started the simulation with the elongated molecular thread and the benzylic amide macrocycle confined on the niradical anion species (see for example the molecular structure depicted in Fig. 1b). Such a choice was imposed by the observed microsecond time scale of the induced shuttling process in solution.13
From Soup: 7 As a first step, to shed some light on the conformations sampled by the reduced form of the rotaxane shown in Fig. 1b , we performed a MD simulation of 100 ns at 298 K in an NVT ensemble and in acetonitrile ( i.e. CH 3 CN) dilute solution. 21 Such a simulation was started considering the molecular shuttle at the centre of a rectangular box of 21 nm 3 filled with solvent molecules at the typical liquid density of 782.2 kg m −3 (see Fig. 1 reported in ESI † ). 21 In this respect, in line with experimental findings, 13 we started the simulation with the elongated molecular thread and the benzylic amide macrocycle confined on the ni radical anion species (see for example the molecular structure depicted in Fig. 1b ). Such a choice was imposed by the observed microsecond time scale of the induced shuttling process in solution. 13
