From Soup: 72 Moreover, as the same authors clearly underlined in that paper, the discovery of the folding/unfolding equilibrium in solution in the case of long and flexible rotaxanes even though of particular interest for people involved in the fabrication and engineering of nano-electromechanical systems, it does not represent an unexpected results since such processes are known in nature (see for example the folding process in proteins ) to be redox controlled 40 .
